the Solamnic Knights.  Even from this distance, the white banner bearing the
kingfisher and the rose can be seen flying high above the keep, calling
attention to the strength and the pride of the Knights of Solamnia.  The open
plain allows the Knights of the Keep to pass to and from the keep with ease.  
